supertzar666 wrote a review Jul 2023
Dunnville, Canada1355 contributions244 helpful votes
+1
Great location
We stayed here for 4 nights recently but through Airbnb and not directly with the hotel. The location is fantastic as it is right across from a beautiful beach and near many restaurants/food vendors. There are 3 restaurants onsite and an amazing roof top infinity pool overlooking the sea. There are a decent amount of chairs but no shade. All areas were very clean and we felt very safe. We will stay here again when in the area.
