Dan N wrote a review Jul 2023
1 contribution1 helpful vote
Great Location, but Nothing Special
Booking a family room for 2 nights. Maybe because my room is on the 6th floor, I could hear all the noise on the street all night long. If you book a room in this hotel, you better get a room in higher floors. Bathroom was small and no bath tub. Sink and countertop both were small. There was not enough space for my personal stuffs. People talked about the infinitive swimming pool. Besides the view, there‚Äôs nothing more to enjoy. Small and narrow, it is more for decoration than for swimming. Breakfast buffet was just ok. Same as other hotels in this area like donuts, cakes, croissants, breads, and some noodles. They provided same foods during my stay. Nothing special.
Date of stay: July 2023
1 Helpful vote
Responded Jul 3, 2023
Dear Mr./ Ms. Dan N, Thank you for leaving a review for our hotel. We are sorry that you did not have a good time at the hotel. In terms of room types, there are currently only 2 types of rooms with bathtubs: Delight City and Delight Ocean. On websites, and booking apps, we already mentioned the bathtub in the description. As for the noise, if you've stayed at the hotel over the past weekend or June 30 - July 1, the music noise comes from the city's event held at the East Sea Park. We apologize for not taking this information when you made your reservation. Once again, √Ä La Carte Da Nang Beach sincerely apologizes to your family for the bad experience during this vacation. Hopefully, our apology can bring some comfort to you and your family. Best Regards, √Ä La Carte Team
