Tania W wrote a review May 2023
Vasse, Australia36 contributions12 helpful votes
Great hotel, great location.
We loved our stay here. It is in a fantastic location right across the road from the beach in the central area. It was a short walk to bats, beach clubs, massages, restaurants, cafes etc and there was a mini Mary just around the corner. The room was spacious and had all the amenities, including flannels and robes. The air-conditioning worked well. Breakfast was awesome with many tastes catered for and eggs how you like, cooked fresh. Our only negative was that there was no shade over the entire pool area. It would have been nice to lay on a lounge up on the roof top, near the pool, but it was too hot in the full sun. We changed cash at the front desk and got a good rate, however, as it was a long weekend we could only change $100 AUD each day (as the banks‚Ä¶
